						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Disch wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Don't ExRAM modes 0 and 1 allow for CPU writing and PPU reading?</div>
<br />Correction: these latches would need to be made of either a buttload of discrete chips or a CPLD <strong>or an ASIC</strong>. MMC5 is such an ASIC. I left off "or an ASIC" because it's unlikely that the homebrew community could design and produce a custom ASIC.</div>

